                                    </p>
                                </support>
                                <extent>Tvíblöðungur í fólíóbroti (<dimensions type="leaf" scope="all" unit="mm">
                                        <height>322</height>
                                        <width>410</width>
                                    </dimensions>). Bl. <locus from="2r" facs="#AMDI-F0075-0041-0002r" to="2v">2</locus> er autt.</extent>
                                <condition>Blöðin eru í góðu ásigkomulagi.</condition>
